{"type": "article", "id": 37886, "title": "Kate Spade 承认出售传闻，以及，Kanye West 的第五季新品有进步｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-02-17T03:12:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 8169, "name": "滑板鞋"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 17749, "name": "yeezy"}, {"id": 2816, "name": "Kate Spade"}, {"id": 6459, "name": "雅芳"}, {"id": 37738, "name": "时代传媒"}, {"id": 2854, "name": "Karlie Kloss"}, {"id": 7113, "name": "Kanye West"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170217104251eZAXwLRC7cYN810I.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/laurengensler/2017/02/16/kate-spade-exploring-strategic-alternatives/#d86775439247\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Kate Spade 承认出售传闻，股票价格随之大涨 11%</strong></a> | 周四，Kate Spade 承认它正在进行战略决策，最坏的结果将是出售。目前，该品牌正在等待第一轮投标，将于本月底之前提交。另外，Kate Spade 还公布了它的第四季度财报，财报显示，它的销售额增长了 10%，至 4.71 亿美元，略低于分析师预测的 4.73 亿美元。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cnbc.com/2017/02/16/avon-shares-plunge-after-earnings-sales-miss-on-weak-demand.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Avon 雅芳集团业绩连续四年下跌</strong></a> | 美国美容产品 Avon 雅芳集团的第四季度财报显示，该公司的业绩下跌了 2.4%，至 15.7 亿美元，低于预期的 16.1 亿美元，2016 年全年总收入为 57.18 亿美元，同比下降了 7.2%，这已经是雅芳集团连续第四年的业绩下跌。周四，该公司的股价大跌了 14%。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cnbc.com/2017/02/16/time-incs-quarterly-revenue-falls-slightly.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>纸媒广告大幅下降，数字广告有所上升，时代集团的第四季度业绩不及预期</strong></a> | 掌管着数家媒体的时代传媒集团日前公布了其第四季度业绩。数据显示，在截至去年 12 月 31 日的三个月内，时代集团销售额同比下跌 1.1% 至 8.67 亿美元，净利润增长至 5600 万美元，但仍不及预期。其中，占据时代集团广告总收入三分之二的纸媒广告下跌 10.2%，数字广告部分收入则取得了 63% 的增长。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/louis-vuitton-pop-up-store-in-ifc-mall\" rel=\"nofollow\">LV 在香港国际金融中心商场开设期间限定店铺</a>。该店铺的外观好似一个玻璃行李箱，在玻璃外墙上印着 LV 2017 春夏男装系列的非洲文化主题元素，包括 Chapman Brothers 所绘的非洲大象、犀牛、长颈鹿及斑马艺术图案，还立了一只长颈鹿雕塑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images medium-insert-images-grid\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100158uAZWVQfTCUFNIcwk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100159LwjsyBXq7r9VDItc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100211tVE4IcjFaye6lQP5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100211mtwasTEG3oPfHBqX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/02/16/yeezy-season-5/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kanye West 发布 了 Yeezy Season 5</a>。这一季囊括了水洗牛仔、做旧、刺绣和迷彩等元素，另有重塑的经典运动服装和 adidas Originals 合作的 Yeezy Runner。比起上一季，这一季明显进步了不少。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images medium-insert-images-grid\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100249N7MhG0pwiEVZ3X48.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201702171002493goTOeKCwu1F2cp7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100249C2dMx9hZ1Ln68ATu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100249vo3ZqEFwluLNgc8d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100250hSTEcKjdouaFmLsY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100250DB6NbSoqRXZIPAiF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201702171002495wctQ7joGy9i8Xz4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201702171002506IfSmrlRBwQJnckV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100250k1Oq2jMIczQe5paH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100251THfE6OLRAiQop4Fy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100251XsB9Dr7EIfCJlVU6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201702171002516YHjMNIs0V5cW8QG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100307wGKrLt6OzyFWTPdo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100317PZWbuqGINYCKBFAH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100318lBZ2TxGn43ueKYya.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/supreme-2017-spring-summer-london-release\" rel=\"nofollow\">Supreme 的 2017 春夏系列首波作品</a>已于周四登陆纽约、洛杉矶、伦敦和巴黎门店。该系列包括印有 Supreme 字样的人造皮草外套、梵高连帽衫、象牙白复古运动套装、牛仔外套和牛仔裤等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images medium-insert-images-grid\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201702171003380kGXh5sYNmCrRKct.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100338FkTPYORDE2oiBfCe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100338dNay0gCTh7kRD14s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100338LzpGumElAZIa6VwH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100338i5NxQAHSYT37R1qI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201702171003385wYoGkLl9DdEasuO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100339AoY7cL9rHMEOx0WZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201702171003391Bow6kKaNIRDMiCZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201702171003390KYvbkI8q75NyB6n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100411N0EU7XkLAwOcnsaW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/adidas-skateboarding-acapulco-slip-on\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Skateboarding 发布全新鞋款 Acapulco</a>。这双鞋以经典的 Penny Loafer 为原型，鞋身以皮革制作，搭载缓震鞋垫和耐磨橡胶鞋底，把皮鞋和滑板鞋完美结合。定价为 80 美元，将于 3 月 1 日起正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images medium-insert-images-grid\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201702171004223ufRLzQKE64cZCVN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100422Bntf2HqmCR8TaPYM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217100423Zk4B2CAqD6xaSPft.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/karlie-kloss-geisha-vogue-march-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">名模 Karlie Kloss 为美国版的《Vogue》三月刊拍摄了一组日本风情的时尚大片</a>。这组照片取景于日本，由摄影师 Mikael Jansson 掌镜， Karlie Kloss 则出境扮演了日本传统艺妓，从造型、场景到服装，都还挺美的。 </p><p>不过，这组照片却在 Instagram 上引起了争论，有些网友觉得，不应该找一个白人来扮演日本艺妓，这是对日本文化的不尊重。并且声称，“如果你想要一个亚洲文化主题，那就应该请个亚洲人”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images medium-insert-images-grid\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217101302eokp43bAVl6dJvHR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217101309xf9gc0zOD4JrUqGQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217101309Ys0wR7yCQvubLI8F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217101309Xryq5GKMFNwEV9ID.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217101315DRj18zZEX7Tvx0mM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217101321RWh5FmAHXBM0rQCk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217101321K3PQ8qgMinsNfWdb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170217101321JKetz4oX2DSFAaCW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/karlie-kloss-geisha-vogue-march-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">popbee</a></p>"}